<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= subject %></title>
  <style>
    /* Modern dark-yellow email theme */

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #0d0f16;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 620px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #151821;
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fcd45b, #fce16e);
      color: #0d0f16;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #fcd45b;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 35px 40px;
    }

    .content h2 {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .content p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #d1d5db;
      margin: 12px 0;
    }

    .days-until {
      background: #1f232d;
      border-left: 4px solid #fcd45b;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      color: #fcd45b;
      font-size: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    .project-info {
      background: #1c1f29;
      border: 1px solid #2d313d;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .project-info h3 {
      color: #fcd45b;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .project-info p {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .info-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: #151821;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #d1d5db;
      border: 1px solid #2d313d;
    }

    .info-item span:first-child {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #fcd45b;
      color: #0d0f16;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      transition: background 0.2s ease;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background: #ffe070;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #11131a;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 25px 15px;
      border-top: 1px solid #2d313d;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .content {
        padding: 25px;
      }

      .info-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .email-container {
        margin: 10px;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Project Reminder</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= memberName %>,</h2>
      <p>This is a friendly reminder about your upcoming project.</p>

      <div class="days-until">
  ‚ö†Ô∏è Project starts in <strong><%= daysUntilStart %></strong> <%= daysUntilStart === 1 ? 'day' : 'days' %>
    </div>


      <div class="project-info">
        <h3><%= projectName %></h3>
        <p><%= projectDescription || 'No description provided' %></p>

        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-item">
            <span>üìÖ</span>
            <span><%= startDate %></span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <span>‚è∞</span>
            <span><%= startHour %>:00 - <%= endHour %>:00</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <span>üìç</span>
            <span><%= location %></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Please review the project details and ensure you're prepared.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated reminder from The Weddx Calendar.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact your Admin.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
